{"serial": "33022", "department_serial": 29, "code": "ME2073", "class": "C", "name": {"en": "Thermodynamics I", "ch": "熱力學(I)"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Tseng, Chung-Jen"], "ch": ["曾重仁"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 1, "session": ["3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "410"}}, {"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["2"]}, "loc": {"building": "E2", "room": "410"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 60, "department": {"ch": "機械工程學系", "en": "Department of Mechanical Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 60, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "熱為能量作用的一種方式，這門課旨在瞭解物理學上的熱現象，進而探討不同形式的能量之間的轉換，因此是能源科技的基礎課程，也介紹應用熱力學的工程實例。學生將能展示以下的能力︰\n1. 從圖表或狀態方程式決定真實物質的性質，例如水蒸氣、冷媒和理想氣體。\n2. 分析在封閉和開放系統中涉及不同工作流體的過程，來決定過程變化關係；和應用熱力學第一定律作能量平衡，來求解熱和功的變化率。\n3. 應用熱力學第二定律分析熱力系統和控制體積。", "en": "Introduction to the concept of energy and the laws governing the transfers and transformations of energy. Emphasis on thermodynamic properties and the first and second law analysis of systems and control volumes. Integration of these concepts into the analysis of basic thermodynamic devices is introduced."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 熱力學簡介與基本概念\n2. 能量、能量分析與熱力學第一定律\n3. 純物質之性質\n4. 封閉系統的能量分析\n5. 控制體積之質量與能量分析\n6. 熱力學第二定律\n7. 熵", "en": "1   Introduction and Basic Concepts\n2   Energy Conversion and General Energy Analysis\n3   Properties of Pure Substances\n4   Energy Analysis of Closed Systems\n5   Mass and Energy Analysis of Control Volumes\n6   The Second Law of Thermodynamics\n7   Entropy"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“教科書：\nCengel, Y. A. and Boles, M. A. (2019) \nThermodynamics: An Engineering Approach,\n9th edition, McGraw-Hill, \nISBN：9781260092684\n東華圖書公司代理，電話：（02）2311-4027 \n(林文隆0932922193) 。\n參考書:\n1. Moran and Shapiro, Fundamentals of Engineering Thermodynamics, 5th Ed., Wiley, 2003.\n2. Sonnta